WEBVTT

00:03.015 --> 00:05.383
♪

00:05.385 --> 00:07.085
MAN (on video):
No! Aah!

00:07.087 --> 00:09.387
(goon laughing)

00:09.389 --> 00:11.389
Don't move.

00:11.391 --> 00:13.591
Shh.

00:16.628 --> 00:19.363
When your people do business
in my territory,

00:19.365 --> 00:22.633
makes me think
you don't respect me.

00:22.635 --> 00:26.204
It was a mistake, I swear.

00:26.206 --> 00:28.272
Maybe so...

00:28.274 --> 00:31.709
but mistakes have consequences.

00:31.711 --> 00:33.845
No, no! No! No, please!

00:33.847 --> 00:35.913
I'm begging you, no! No!

00:35.915 --> 00:37.548
Talk to the hand.

00:37.550 --> 00:39.350
(screams)

00:39.352 --> 00:42.520
(sighs) Think I'll skip
the ending this time.

00:42.522 --> 00:44.655
I just had breakfast.

00:44.657 --> 00:45.957
My point, exactly, Judge.

00:45.959 --> 00:47.592
Allowing the jury
to see this video

00:47.594 --> 00:49.060
would be grossly
prejudicial.

00:49.062 --> 00:50.561
I agree with the gross part.

00:50.563 --> 00:53.598
Maybe your client should stop
torturing the competition.

00:53.600 --> 00:56.901
It is exceedingly graphic
and disturbing, Counselor.

00:56.903 --> 00:58.669
Well, they don't call her
the Lioness for nothing.

00:58.671 --> 01:01.005
Ms. Chao is the most dangerous
human trafficker in New York.

01:01.007 --> 01:02.173
Allegedly.

01:02.175 --> 01:04.675
She smuggles desperate
immigrants into the country

01:04.677 --> 01:06.911
and then sells them
into sex slavery.

01:06.913 --> 01:08.713
We're all aware of the charges,
Ms. Reagan.

01:08.715 --> 01:11.315
Which includes assault
in the first degree,

01:11.317 --> 01:13.885
which this tape depicts
in spades.

01:13.887 --> 01:15.386
My client can not get
a fair trial

01:15.388 --> 01:17.388
if this tape is admitted,
Your Honor.

01:17.390 --> 01:19.223
The authenticity of this tape
is not in dispute,

01:19.225 --> 01:21.392
and its probative value
is obvious.

01:21.394 --> 01:23.161
I am concerned about
the sensational nature

01:23.163 --> 01:24.796
of the video.
Thank you.

01:24.798 --> 01:27.331
It speaks directly
to the heinous nature

01:27.333 --> 01:29.767
of the alleged crime,
Your Honor.

01:29.769 --> 01:31.569
And while potentially
prejudicial,

01:31.571 --> 01:34.138
its probative value
is undeniable.

01:35.240 --> 01:37.108
I'm gonna allow it
into evidence.

01:37.976 --> 01:39.477
Thank you, Your Honor.

01:39.479 --> 01:42.280
Due respect, Your Honor,
this is totally unfair.

01:42.282 --> 01:43.848
I'm sure the
one-handed gentleman

01:43.850 --> 01:46.484
in the video
felt the same way.

01:50.222 --> 01:52.456
FRANK: Excuse me.
Are you listening?

01:52.458 --> 01:54.058
I asked you to set up
a press conference.

01:54.096 --> 01:54.695
I heard.

01:54.707 --> 01:56.161
I would have thought
he'd be thrilled.

01:56.162 --> 01:57.995
Seeing as you spend
half your days

01:57.997 --> 01:59.297
trying to push him in there.

01:59.299 --> 02:00.431
And normally, I would be.

02:00.433 --> 02:01.365
Normally?

02:01.367 --> 02:02.867
I think we should take a beat.

02:02.869 --> 02:04.435
Oh, I see what he's doing.

02:04.437 --> 02:06.404
Who you got him on?
One of the morning shows?

02:06.406 --> 02:07.839
GARRETT: No.
- <i>Charlie Rose?</i>

02:07.841 --> 02:10.041
<i>Charlie Rose</i> would be a great
platform to roll this out.

02:10.043 --> 02:11.742
No. Not <i>Charlie Rose.</i>

02:11.744 --> 02:14.846
Not anybody.
You're sitting on something.

02:15.981 --> 02:19.550
The acting mayor,
she opposes the plan.

02:24.823 --> 02:28.659
Oh, come on, Garrett.
It's a gift to her.

02:28.661 --> 02:30.027
Apparently, she doesn't
see it that way.

02:30.029 --> 02:31.863
In what way does she see it?

02:31.865 --> 02:33.130
She thinks the cost of
retraining officers

02:33.132 --> 02:34.332
is prohibitive.

02:34.334 --> 02:35.800
Oh, please.
GORMLEY: How the hell would she know?

02:35.802 --> 02:39.036
Dutton was a dog catcher
till 15 minutes ago.

02:39.038 --> 02:41.472
Public advocate,
and she believes the program

02:41.474 --> 02:43.541
prioritizes targeting
street crime...

02:43.543 --> 02:45.209
And when's the last time
somebody got mugged

02:45.211 --> 02:46.777
on the street by Bernie Madoff?

02:46.779 --> 02:49.480
She's missing the whole point.

02:49.482 --> 02:53.150
We should cancel your morning
and schedule a face-to-face...

02:53.152 --> 02:56.487
I already sold that
and she's not buying.

